column2: Floating grass- 90 F- water temp: 68 F (11')
Early June- green floating blobs were evident on surface.  These gradually sunk to bottom.  Very few evident 7/2/95.
Green water unusual for this time of year.  Some algae on top.
Cloudy and windy.  2.4 inches of rain last week.
Overcast.  Over 12" of rain in the last 2 weeks.
sunny and cool 57 F. frost warning
Loons have already left the lake.
twin baby loons on the lake
